{"tid":1786412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警拒透露OT上限時數","createTime":"2019-12-17T06:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T06:56:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fb15b1e8b8cad5a3b3821795bffdd854d268bd","tid":1786412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/TPTD4YWZ5CKCDUS62BGHJND75Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FTPTD4YWZ5CKCDUS62BGHJND75Y%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0gpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=f09ebba6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FTPTD4YWZ5CKCDUS62BGHJND75Y%2F&h=6bafacd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/TPTD4YWZ5CKCDUS62BGHJND75Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n警拒透露OT上限時數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191217/large/1576514619_d05e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576514619_d05e.gif&h=d51ffb8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警隊6月至11月的超時補水達9.5億元，平均每月領取人數達1.1萬人。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處6月至11月超時補水達9.5億元，民主派質疑警方未公佈至少九項額外津貼數目。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓辯稱，有關津貼為恒常津貼，與行動無關，金額已涵蓋在每年預算中，拒絕披露數字，並拒透露現時警方最高超時工作時數。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：錯用李寶安 買星美債券勁蝕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱每年預算已涵蓋津貼<br />\n<br />\n保安局早前披露，6月至11月警隊的超時補水達9.5億元，平均每月領取人數達1.1萬人。但根據《公務員事務規例》，每月超時工作不可多於60小時，因應特殊、緊急或真正有需要情況下才可超出此限。<br />\n<br />\n被問到警隊現時的逾時工作上限時數為多少，郭嘉銓拒絕透露數字，僅稱警方每月檢討有關上限，視乎當月工作情況及行動需要調整，並謂警員一般超時工作會先以補假補償，如果無法補假，才按《公務員事務規例》及警隊內部規條，發放紀律部隊逾時工作津貼。<br />\n<br />\n對於民主派質疑警方未有交代至少九項津貼金額，推斷實際補貼金額更高，郭嘉銓同樣拒絕披露有關數字，但承認除了紀律部隊逾時工作津貼外，警員亦有不同津貼，因部份工作較危險艱辛，如飛虎隊要潛水等，「呢啲津貼係恒常，唔係同呢次嘅特別行動有關」，有關津貼金額已涵蓋在每年預算中。<br />\n<br />\n警方自6月行動至今合共拘捕6,105人，當中978人被檢控，上周共有99人被捕，單計前日被捕人數為31人，包括17名學生；彈藥使用方面，警方上周一使用兩發橡膠子彈，前日至昨日凌晨共使用27枚催淚彈及3發橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李詠希、曾偉龍"},{"pid":"b10333da6448083eca9d7d767fc39451fb15127f","tid":1786412,"uid":293291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"因為冇上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e72f134aeb561810a67ce8e700235dd5e1ff44","tid":1786412,"uid":69611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"8月份係狗屋聽過150小時<br />\n唔知白衫係咪一樣"},{"pid":"f1b1742b36f82193dd9ceb0a38972c7d932238c4","tid":1786412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2528f7267d22901535481f7d1c4ae94d4d610200","tid":1786412,"uid":68038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"更方便呃ot錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母btw"},{"pid":"4764008d5c4e2ce96c81882c376511786f22e370","tid":1786412,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差1萬5千人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/do